description: Sunny East-Side 2 bed, 1 bath apartment located directly across from the ocean, available June 1st. At the corner of Farragut and East 6th in South Boston's highly-coveted Castle Island neighborhood, this second floor unit boasts water views from every window. The front door opens to a spacious living area, an attached eat-in kitchen with a designated dining area, and one king and one queen-sized bedroom. Moments from Marine Park, Memorial Rink, Pleasure Bay, and Castle Island, this freshly painted apartment includes generous closet space, updated appliances, and a resident-only landscaped garden courtyard that blooms throughout the warmer months - not to mention easy street parking on this side of Southie. Heat, hot water, trash and snow removal are included in the rent, as well as convenient on-site laundry facilities.
